{"tid":1501624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再叫人唔去遊行入機場","createTime":"2019-08-24T12:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T15:45:24.000Z","uid":212646,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af966f0aaded1a027e307def2cd6ae6aac923070","tid":1501624,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:01:00.000Z","msg":"無遊行嘅手足幫你持續抗爭make noise<br />\n根本唔會多人入機場<br />\n你地叫人唔去荃葵青<br />\n大部分人只會直接唔出<br />\n而唔會轉去機場<br />\n813已經係實例"},{"pid":"ee292b7e58dd382dfd0e9696d6bcbb8e21f79537","tid":1501624,"uid":212646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:03:25.000Z","msg":"入機場係正確<br />\n但唔係乜計劃都無就叫人入<br />\n今日約7點？搞手諗乜？<br />\n7點就算係民陣大遊行都無可能多人啦<br />\n就算612 7點多人，但都做唔到阻塞交通"},{"pid":"381791159c60b508bf554741653b904981b721d7","tid":1501624,"uid":212646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:06:13.000Z","msg":"仲有遊行搞手承擔風險搞左咁耐<br />\n你地一句轉場，人地一少人<br />\n一係就出左嘅人送死<br />\n一係就嗰區嘅手足心灰意冷<br />\n好老實講，機場係王牌，幾時搞都有效<br />\n但地區遊行唔係<br />\n你睇元朗咁，只要衰過一次，而家成區永不超生咁"},{"pid":"7a08a80d2953f230bbad40826f481fa02403b54c","tid":1501624,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:13:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40d20294ae1754ebce499798780cbeb56d27fc9e","tid":1501624,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:30:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d69a587e34f2b659f51d89ddc54bbf78a181befd","tid":1501624,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:46:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"115264c5d08c812d8cb7aa156b7e5a5ae08b62c6","tid":1501624,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:46:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18aaf9354541bac8e49699c8c4371dba17a9a018","tid":1501624,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:46:59.000Z","msg":"荃葵青手足唔係condom"},{"pid":"21f9cbadc9d6cacf1f1a919862674c408c1bc8bc","tid":1501624,"uid":212646,"like